  <name>Plom Client</name>
  <summary>Grading/marking client for the Plom online grading system</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Plom is a system for giving tests on paper, but marking and
      returning them online.  This is the graphical interface used
      for grading marking tests.
    </p>
  </description>

